## Version History

### v1.2.0 (2026-06-14)
**Checkboxes (Multiple Choice) Question Type**

New Features:
- Added Checkboxes (Multiple Choice) question type
- Multiple answer selection with single submit action
- Full support across survey editor, embed widget, and response analytics
- Aggregated display of multi-select answers in response viewer

### v1.1.1 (2026-06-11)
**Blurr Deployment & Branding**

- Deployed to surveys.blurr-marketing.cloud (new VPS)
- Blurr Surveys branding on login and dashboard
- Fixed missing timing_mode and scroll_percentage DB columns

### v0.1.0 (2026-02-04)
**Initial Release with Security Hardening**

Security Features:
- Domain validation with Origin/Referer checks
- Three-tier rate limiting (global, per-IP, per-site)
- Request body limits and Zod validation
- Input cleanup with safe output rendering
- Database length constraints
- Production HTTPS setup with Caddy

Core Features:
- Multi-tenant survey platform
- Multiple question types (radio, checkbox, text, rating)
- Display settings and targeting rules
- Event tracking (impressions, responses, dismissals)
- Geo-location detection
- Email invitations via SMTP (Hostinger)
- Real-time analytics and reporting
- Background job processing with BullMQ

Admin Features:
- Site management with domain security
- Survey builder with question editor
- Response analytics with charts
- Team management
- My Surveys / All Surveys filtering

Technical:
- FastifyAPI backend with TypeScript
- Vue.js admin frontend
- PostgreSQL database
- Redis for caching and queues
- Docker containerization
- Automated migrations
